product.title: Sakura Butterfly Gold-plated Adjustable Rings | NEW
product.body_html:
Affordable and durable rings ready to dazzle up your style

This Sakura Ring is a beautiful and elegant accessory for any occasion. These adjustable rings feature a delicate butterfly design with a blue sakura blossom. The rings are made of high-quality copper with 18k gold plating and are adjustable to fit almost all finger sizes.

Whether you want to treat yourself or surprise someone special, these rings are a perfect choice. The Sakura Blossom and Butterfly are a symbol of grace, beauty, and transformation. Order yours today and enjoy the compliments!

  • Shape: Sakura & Butterfly
  • Size: Adjustable
  • Metal Type: Copper
  • Material: 18K Real Gold-Plating
  • Category: Rings
  • Package includes: 1 Ring Only
  • Packaging: Rings do not come with the original box to protect the environment but they do come in a plastic bag. Let's save our planet together from unnecessary waste.
  • Maintenance: 18k gold-plated jewelry will not fade. If the color becomes darker, wash it with soap to restore the brightness. Do not wash your hands with the ring on. 

Elevate your jewelry collection today with rings from www.kawaiies.com!
